{"tid":2362201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【無品鄰居】葵盛西邨婆婆晾衫架曬臘鴨　樓下住戶超崩潰：仲滴緊血水","createTime":"2021-01-11T09:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T07:01:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":166,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"7f0fd755c9530629f01cbc7c08a8ab3597e3eaf2","tid":2362201,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"疫情下，市民都較以往注重個人衛生，但總有人做出罔顧公德心的行為。近日有葵盛西邨住戶於網上發文抱怨，指住在樓上的婆婆在晾衫架曬臘鴨，更有血水滴落，令她大感崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n日前有網民於上周四（7日）在Facebook群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」發文，指葵盛西邨8座有位婆婆竟在晾衫架上曬臘鴨。<br />\n&quot;樓上個婆婆晾啲咁既野出嚟，仲滴緊血水，真係想點呢？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n從圖片可見，有人於晾衫架上掛了4隻鴨，並用晾衫夾著一塊紙皮，以覆蓋、保護臘鴨，避免弄髒。樓主留言補充，由於向保安員投訴後未能解決，故打算向區議員求助。<br />\n<br />\n帖文引起熱議，不少網民留言批評婆婆的行為自私兼不衞生，「驚人整污糟佢啲嘢，就唔驚自己啲嘢整污糟人哋啲衫，自私到」，亦有人笑言是「非法處理屍體.....」、「屍體發現案」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2849497/duck_thumb_20210111_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2849497%2Fduck_thumb_20210111_S_1024.jpg&h=f054e107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2849497/134920810_10221243285824824_5582518749576699251_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2849497%2F134920810_10221243285824824_5582518749576699251_n_1024.jpg&h=b6d049c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2849497/134642095_10221243286064830_5601463807396421556_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2849497%2F134642095_10221243286064830_5601463807396421556_n_1024.jpg&h=25f916b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"545e4a8068166f95fa6226c9040bbb696ce400ad","tid":2362201,"uid":107656,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:33:1