d487","tid":2362201,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T23:44:19.000Z","msg":"公屋揸林寶個d唔講？"},{"pid":"77df331c550bf494676f31280bdf9d794749033f","tid":2362201,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f8b5bff4aafcac75838afb9d5ae845cd4eade6f","tid":2362201,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"曬臘鴨曬咸魚<br />\n公屋最興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T23:46:37.000Z","msg":"我老母唔係住公屋都係咁。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0ce3d980bd8d4705590335eb4879478d749ab5","tid":2362201,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T23:46:42.000Z","msg":"葵盛西邨好多精神病人<br />\n因為近葵涌醫院"},{"pid":"429494a8c79c821b1166ed2d99bbdae310e4c137","tid":2362201,"uid":384421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f0fd755c9530629f01cbc7c08a8ab3597e3eaf2","tid":2362201,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"疫情下，市民都較以往注重個人衛生，但總有人做出罔顧公德心的行為。近日有葵盛西邨住戶於網上發文抱怨，指住在樓上的婆婆在晾衫架曬臘鴨，更有血水滴落，令她大感崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n日前有網民於上周四（7日）在Facebook群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」發文，指葵盛西邨8座有位婆婆竟在晾衫架上曬臘鴨。<br />\n&quot;樓上個婆婆晾啲咁既野出嚟，仲滴緊血水，真係想點呢？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n從圖片可見，有人於晾衫架上掛了4隻鴨，並用晾衫夾著一塊紙皮，以覆蓋、保護臘鴨，避免弄髒。樓主留言補充，由於向保安員投訴後未能解決，故打算向區議員求助。<br />\n<br />\n帖文引起熱議，不少網民留言批評婆婆的行為自私兼不衞生，「驚人整污糟佢啲嘢，就唔驚自己啲嘢整污糟人哋啲衫，自私到」，亦有人笑言是「非法處理屍體.....」、「屍體發現案」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2849497/duck_thumb_20210111_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2849497%2Fduck_thumb_20210111_S_1024.jpg&h=f054e107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2849497/134920810_10221243285824824_5582518749576699251_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2849497%2F134920810_10221243285824824_5582518749576699251_n_1024.jpg&h=b6d049c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2849497/134642095_10221243286064830_5601463807396421556_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2849497%2F134642095_10221243286064830_5601463807396421556_n_1024.jpg&h=25f916b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:15:34.000Z","msg":"一般建議<br />\n當你以為接近收成期<br />\n點知先泥比天災人煱毁滅係最撚傷心<br />\n屎尿屁有撚用咩<br />\n丫婆教落 沖沖水就食得啦<br />\n長竹加把刀<br />\n整哂落平台<br />\n等撚左咁耐<br />\n有得睇<br />\n無得食<br />\n再報警有人亂扔蠟鴨<br />\n拎反你張相做證<br />\n到時可以直接換鄰居<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8bb12c463c40daa170447775908200f5555bff","tid":2362201,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:32:39.000Z","msg":"屌，我啲廢老都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2b18b04c08acc1b10ecf9ca491ff7018aa998a","tid":2362201,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:42:43.000Z","msg":"血水事小，滴油既話你啲衫唔洗要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68efe397cfde72b83ec1713de17f3a76d20691d2","tid":2362201,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfb4e92a1dafbcb43f08b178a47c55a13f1bf8e3","tid":2362201,"uid":194298,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:11:58.000Z","msg":"上樓打撚柒佢就岩<br />\n依D一定要你癲過佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:47:35.000Z","msg":"香港人得把口反抗<br />\n實際行動不了"}]}